title: Marriage Built to Last [Pastor Billy Crone]
description:
This is a compilation of Pastor Billy Crone teaching about marriage, the biblical idea of marriage and what God wants out of our marriages or our future marriages. Truly inspiring, something to look at. Of course, following the Bible is what matters but he definitely gives some insight. Highly recommend you purchase the DVD of this or watch it online but this is a compilation that I made of it. Rather big file. Please continue to seed. Thanks. Link: http://www.niagarafrontierbible.com/catalog/cat_relation.php

Thanks and God bless.
